<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>RNOC</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <link href="/assets/css/rnoc.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-inner navbar-fixed-top">
          <div class="pull-left">
            <a href="/"><img src="<%= RNOC[:logo] %>" id="rnoc-logo"></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
<br>
<br>
<br>
      <%= yield %>


    <!-- Help/More information -->
    <div id="myModal" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
        <h3 id="myModalLabel">About RNOC</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>
          <b>RNOC</b> is a <b>N</b>etwork <b>O</b>perations <b>C</b>onsole
          written in Ruby on Rails. RNOC was originally a project
          at <a href="http://www.redhat.com">Red Hat</a>, which is
          where the <b>R</b> in the title comes from.
        </p>

        <h3>Getting Help/Reporting Bugs</h3>

        <ul>
	  <li><a href="https://github.com/Brofaces/rnoc/"><i class="icon-home"></i> RNOC project page on GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/Brofaces/rnoc/issues"><i class="icon-fire"></i> Issue Tracker on GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Credits</h4>

	<ul>
	  <li>
	    <b>RNOC</b> was originally written
	    by <a href="https://github.com/tbielawa">Tim Bielawa</a>,
	    <a href="https://github.com/abutcher">Andrew Butcher</a>,
	    and <a href="https://github.com/yithian">Alex Chvatal</a>
	  </li>
	</ul>

	<p>
	  <b>RNOC</b> is Copyright &copy; 2012-2013 Red Hat Inc.
	</p>

      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>




  </body>
</html>
